title: Artist: Flo Rida
text:
Artist: Flo Rida
Did you know?
Respectable by The Outsiders was written by Ronald Isley, Rudolph Isley, O'Kelly Isley and was first released by The Isley Brothers in 1959.
The Outsiders released it on the audio album Album #2 in 1966.
It was also covered by The Yardbirds, The Chants, The Fourmost and 2 others.
